OL,5, Thousands of households have had their 
OL,6, addresses unknowingly used by crime    
OL,7, gangs to register bogus companies, a   
OL,8, BBC investigation has revealed.        
OL,10,FBBC Radio 4's You and Yours found about
OL,11,F150,000 had been registered and in some
OL,12,Fstreets, every home had been targeted. 
OL,14,FThe residents have then had to deal    
OL,15,Fwith overdrafts, loans, insurance      
OL,16,Fdemands and credit card debts.         
OL,18,FA Companies House spokesman said there 
OL,19,Fwere currently "no legal powers to     
OL,20,Fverify or validate" a firm's details.  
